The ultimate vision for agentic infrastructure is the "Mute Agent"—a system that acts silently and correctly because it understands context so deeply it doesn't need to ask. By implementing this tiered, verified memory framework, we move past the era of chatty assistants into the era of autonomous, persistent partners.
